item.description:
@lolwtfbbqhax wrote:

very nice explanation Mod tainted =.=… and you want to be a mod… pathetic…
you got to make a “case”
so u get the i.d of the portal you spawned and in your client.java
with your other “cases” you put:
case “idofportalhere”:
teleportToX = “coordshere”;
teleportToY = “coordshere”;
sendMessage(“putinalilmessagehere ;)”);
break;

for example ill show you a portal i made that teleported me to this dungeon… PS: it has a strength level requirement^.^

case 7289: if(playerLevel[2] < 110) { sendMessage("You must be 110 Strength to get to the Gargoyles"); } else { teleportToX = 2717; teleportToY = 9816; sendMessage("Good Luck on that Mouse toy!!"); } break;

PS: hope this was of some help! and Mod Tainted… i think you should learn more java
